---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout active="network" title="Adamant — Peer map" description="Geographic and ASN distribution of validators and service nodes. Residential-fibre claim, in numbers.">
  <section class="page-intro">
    <div class="container">
      <div>
        <div class="crumb">§ Explorer · /network/peers</div>
        <h1 class="title">Peer map.</h1>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="lede">Adamant's residential-fibre commitment is auditable. The peer map shows where validators and service nodes operate, by country and by ASN — without exposing IP addresses or operator identities.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr; gap: 32px;" class="net-grid">
        <div style="border: 1px solid var(--ink); padding: 28px; min-height: 360px; background: repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, transparent 0 18px, rgba(255,255,255,0.04) 18px 19px); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;">
          <span class="serif" style="font-size: 22px; font-style: italic; color: var(--ink-3);">Map renders at testnet activation.</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div style="border: 1px solid var(--rule); background: var(--paper);">
            <div style="padding: 12px 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);"><span class="label">ASN distribution · pre-launch</span></div>
            <div style="padding: 32px 16px; color: var(--ink-3); font-family: var(--serif); font-style: italic;">No validators yet.</div>
          </div>
          <div style="border: 1px solid var(--rule); background: var(--paper); margin-top: 18px;">
            <div style="padding: 12px 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);"><span class="label">Connection type</span></div>
            <div style="padding: 18px 16px;">
              <div style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between;" class="mono small">
                <span>Residential fibre</span><span>—</span>
              </div>
              <div style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; margin-top: 6px;" class="mono small">
                <span>Datacentre</span><span>—</span>
              </div>
              <div style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; margin-top: 6px;" class="mono small">
                <span>Other</span><span>—</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="small" style="margin-top: 18px;">Operators self-declare their connection type; the chain does not verify it cryptographically. Truthful disclosure is a community norm, audited by collective observation rather than enforcement.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
